==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Matchable
<hw>Match"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of being
matched; comparable on equal conditions; adapted to being joined
together; correspondent.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Match"a*ble*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sir Walter Raleigh . . . is <qex>matchable</qex> with the best of
the ancients.</q> <rj><qau>Hakewill.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>matchboard</ent>⟦br⟧
